{"tid":2513944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"環保團體揭中共喺東南亞投資煤炭電廠 疑輸出高污染產業外判海外滿足其零碳承諾","createTime":"2021-05-03T02:43:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T07:19:28.000Z","uid":52779,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"67deb302d78e154edae4059350d4298bbdcfb6df","tid":2513944,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T02:43:19.000Z","msg":"中共雖然大玩「氣候牌」，聲稱會在2060年前達致零碳，但不少環保團體近期揭發中共正積極投資印尼、越南、柬埔寨和老撾等東南亞國家的煤炭發電廠，加劇當地污染，引發當地居民不滿，同時將高污染產業外判海外，從而滿足其零碳承諾。<br />\n<br />\n能源與清潔空氣研究中心（CREA）表示，中國現時是東南亞煤炭的主要投資國，在中國海外煤炭投資組合當中，印尼及越南是中共全球第二和第三大投資最多的國家，而煤炭發電分別佔印尼及越南當地用電量的56％及34.3％。<br />\n<br />\n不單是電廠，中資金融機構亦參與這些高污染產業，多個國際環保團體早前發表《Banking on Climate Chaos》報告，當中批評中國建設銀行、中銀、工行和農行等，都是投資燃煤發電的前11大銀行、投資煤礦開採的十大金融機構之一，令人質疑中共所謂「零碳」目標，以及中港日夜吹墟的「綠色金融」徒具形式。<br />\n<br />\n中共透過一帶一路融資，將高污染發電模式輸出海外，已令當地大感不滿，當中反對中資煤炭項目的印尼NGO表示，相關計劃一來污染當地空氣及水，危害居民健康，二來令當地過份依賴中資煤炭，更難發展出可再生能源，三來這些煤炭發電廠往往可經營長達50年，這意味東南亞各國須長期為中國的「dirty energy（骯髒能源）」付出成本，造成沉重財政負擔。<br />\n<br />\n如大部分一帶一路項目一樣，中資煤炭廠往往用中國工人、中國承包商、中國技術，當地受惠有限，加上一切污染、環境破壞、健康問題則要當地社會承受，令人質疑中共官媒經常宣稱「一帶一路創造雙贏」，明顯只是謊言。<br />\n<br />\n今次不是首次中共海外項目被指破壞全球環境，早前外媒亦報道過中共在巴爾干半島的煤炭投資，令當地出現北京式陰霾。隨着本身污染問題嚴重的中共忽然以「環保大國」自居，各地環團更加積極揭發全球環保問題背後「中國因素」，相信這類有關中共如何透過「一帶一路」輸出污染的報道將會越來越多。<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://twitter.com/MekongEye/status/1388724134100692994\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMekongEye%2Fstatus%2F1388724134100692994&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGtSHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=7fe02870\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMekongEye%2Fstatus%2F1388724134100692994&h=5d0a2c09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/MekongEye/status/1388724134100692994</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SCMPNews/status/1388874773292257284\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSCMPNews%2Fstatus%2F1388874773292257284&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGtSHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=f38f73cf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSCMPNews%2Fstatus%2F1388874773292257284&h=5149fef2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SCMPNews/status/1388874773292257284</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://asiatimes.com/2020/12/chinese-investment-puts-a-cloud-over-the-balkans/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fasiatimes.com%2F2020%2F12%2Fchinese-investment-puts-a-cloud-over-the-balkans%2F&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGtSHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=065ae8a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://asiatimes.com/2020/12/chinese-investment-puts-a-cloud-over-the-balkans/</a></blockquote><br />\n</blockquote><br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://t.me/HKinternationalfront/699\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKinternationalfront%2F699&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGtSHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=48685c11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKinternationalfront/699</a>"},{"pid":"9ee523bc47ff2111de4666d6d2293f2efa82dad4","tid":2513944,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T02:43:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hair.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fb3e3602ac9c60b5e13982f3d85880a45065554","tid":2513944,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T02:43:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4bc81b6f7c45ceeda5a9478a1a5a1173a9e10eae","tid":2513944,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ee523bc47ff2111de4666d6d2293f2efa82dad4","tid":2513944,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T02:43:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hair.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T02:44:02.000Z","msg":"你真係好快手"},{"pid":"2faf001883d806999045c0ba30b345bd9d89fb59","tid":2513944,"uid":51346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4bc81b6f7c45ceeda5a9478a1a5a1173a9e10eae","tid":2513944,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ee523bc47f